events.title: Community Hours
events.description: Join us for our weekly community hours at Initial Research's SoHo space. The space is available for co-working, meetings, and conversations with our fellows during weekday programs. Wi-Fi, a growing collection of books, and tea are provided. No RSVP is necessary—just stop by and say hello!
